        <updateDate>2004-07-26T17:10:59Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Designates September 2004 as Service for Seniors Month.</p> <p>Recognizes the need for companionship and assistance with daily tasks among seniors with long-term health conditions throughout the year. Encourages: (1) the people of the United States to volunteer regularly with homebound frail elderly or at a nursing home or long-term care facility; (2) volunteer organizations that offer companionship and assistance to seniors to incorporate Service for Seniors Month in their recruitment efforts; and (3) individuals to volunteer in these service organizations.</p> <p></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
